<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٠٩١ - وَقَالَ لِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1822">خَلِيفَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7069">يَزِيدُ بْنُ زُرَيْعٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2332">سَعِيدٌ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6257">وَمُعْتَمِرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2609">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>حَدَّثَهُمْ عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِهَذَا وَقَالَ <span class="c2">«عَائِذًا بِاللهِ مِنْ شَرِّ الْفِتَنِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>